changeSet.sql:
COMMENT ON VIEW v_country_statistics IS 'Aggregated statistics by country: agreement count, premium totals and averages.
FIXED (refactoring plan, p. 3.4): Countries are filtered to current active versions only: c.valid_from <= CURRENT_DATE AND (c.valid_to IS NULL OR c.valid_to >= CURRENT_DATE)
Without this fix, a country with multiple temporal versions would appear multiple times in the statistics, each with a partial count of agreements.';
